data.description:
***Back on Market- Seller did not receive deposit***Welcome to this exquisite custom-built brick home,  situated just a block away from the serene Lakefront Levee Trail. This stately residence boasts a seamless floorplan designed for effortless entertaining, featuring multiple living spaces.
As you step into the grand foyer, your gaze is drawn upward to the soaring 17-foot ceiling, adorned by a dazzling crystal chandelier. The first level offers a versatile layout with a formal living and dining area, a generously sized den complete with a brick fireplace, wet bar, and direct access to both the kitchen and picturesque backyard.
There's plenty of room in the bright and spacious kitchen which includes all appliances, a large island, breakfast bar, pantry, plenty of cabinets (with pull out shelving) and expansive counter space.  A first-floor study provides versatile work or study options. Upstairs, discover 5 spacious bedrooms, including the primary suite with an abundance of closet space. Step into your private oasis in the backyard, where a refreshing pool and covered patio invite relaxation and outdoor gatherings. Rear yard access leads to a generously sized detached 2-car garage, complete with a practical mini kitchen and half bath. Above the garage, a second-floor bonus room awaits your creativity, great for a guest suite, workshop, or fitness area. Recent updates include a 2 year old roof with 30-year lifetime shingles offering peace of mind.
Embrace the lifestyle you deserve in this meticulously crafted residence offering an abundance of comforts and possibilities.
